Source: qrreader
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: QR Reader Maintainer <qrreader@localhost>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), file
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/example/qr-reader-u22

Package: qrreader
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: polkitd
Description: QR/barcode serial reader (PyInstaller binary)
 Standalone qrreader executable: reads serial scanner data, transliterates
 Serbian Cyrillic to Latin, pastes into the active window.
 .
 Configure port in /etc/qrreader/port. Enable per-user service:
 systemctl --user enable --now qrreader.service
